g to be clear or interesting.  Sometimes a pillars hitbox is in the way, doesnt look like it, but it is, and youll take a massive hit for something that wasnt entirely your fault. Not to mention its just not satisying, when enemies die, its so unsatisfying, as theyre all just tiny nothings on your screen. Speaking of unsatisfying...4. music/asthetic: the music is bland and boring. Maybe itl get better later, im gonna play more so heres hoping it does. this however just underscores a generally bland and uninteresting aethetic. The game is afraid to stray too far from the arcade versions original look, failing completely to realise that it existed out of limitations in tech, not choice. Dark legacy had style, vast different styles even. Maybe this game picks that up later, but the first set of levels is so dreadfully nothing, idk what they were even going for. It just doesnt bode well. if this is their attempt to hook me in, its not doing a good job.still, im hoping things pick up, and im hoping its more fun with friends. gonna keep playing, but if your on the fence. maybe hold off, do more research. let the hype leave ur system a bit, then look into it."
